name: Live Technician
overview: Live-technician is a firm dealing in computer technical support. The California, US based firm with branches sprang up in United Kingdom, Canada and assistance delivered worldwide stands acclaimed for its remarkably well services. The firm has been long known for technical professional assistance it renders to its customers. The supreme customer support is rendered for technical glitches occurring in PC, laptops ultra-books, net books for all brands and also the assistance stretches to peripherals and iPhones. The operating system issues, browser conflicts and many other snags with computer’s hardware and software are skillfully taken care of by the experts at the firm. The technical services of the syndicate are conceivable round the clock, from corner to corner. The Microsoft certified trained experts assure comprehensive assistance to the users.
